### Register as EMPLOYER
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "apple@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Apple",
  "lastName": "HR",
  "bio": "Apple is looking for talented engineers to join our team.",
  "userType": "EMPLOYER"
}

